    "• Conscious consideration and thorough thinking before an article is liked or shared, or a headline is taken at face value • Utilizes an individual's knowledge, abilities, and attitudes to critically evaluate (media-communicated) information based on specific criteria including credibility, source, and quality",
    "Individuals' confidence in their ability to detect manipulative messages, participate in social discourses, and actively position themselves against disinformation is cultivated through empowerment strategies and methods:",
    "• A certain form of behavior that encompasses a person's ability to recognize and state doubts about specific content as well as express their own thoughts.",
    "Empowerment relies on individuals' knowledge (awareness) and analytical thinking (reflection) regarding messages conveyed through the media.",
    "Moreover, it could also be a factor that anticipates increased awareness."
  ],
